### ========== 4. TEST SAU KHI LOGIN ==========

### 4.1 Get current user info (thay YOUR_TOKEN bằng token từ response trên)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4.2 Register Customer mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newcustomer",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "newcustomer@example.com",
  "full_name": "Khách Hàng Mới",
  "phone": "0901234567"
}

### 4.3 Register Staff mới (cần admin token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/staff
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newstaff",
  "password": "staff123",
  "email": "newstaff@supermarket.com",
  "full_name": "Nhân Viên Mới",
  "position": "Cashier",
  "employment_type": "full-time"
}

